        public boolean wantsPartialMessages()
        Flag for a onMessage() that wants partial messages.

        This indicates the use of MessageHandler.Partial.

        Returns:
        true for use of MessageHandler.Partial, false for use of MessageHandler.Whole

      • wantsStreams

        public boolean wantsStreams()
        Flag for a onMessage() method that wants MessageHandler.Whole with a Decoder that is based on TextStream or BinaryStream
        Returns:
        true for Streaming based Decoder, false for normal decoder for whole messages.
